overview: They're back! The horny students we met in Catalina's successful movie continue their antics in Scott Masters' HEAD OF THE CLASS II. New sensation Adam Grant is an A+ handsome and hung. Join Adam and classmen Beau Beaumont, Chris Dano, Chris Ladd, and many more collegiate hunks as they "cram" for exams in an unforgettable climax... HEAD OF THE CLASS II from Catalina Video: The ultimate homecoming!
title: Head of the Class 2
